==Description==
The '''Everstone''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The '''Everstone''' has a value of 3 [[Diamonds]] {{Diamonds}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals.

==Mine Layout==
The Everstone appears in the Underground as a 3x2 sized object.<br><br>
